    CompCRDs -->|watched by| MCCtrl
    CompCRDs -->|watched by| TrainCtrl
    CompCRDs -->|watched by| FeastCtrl
    CompCRDs -->|watched by| LlamaCtrl

    %% Gateway creates infrastructure
    GatewayCtrl -->|creates| GW["data-science-gateway<br/>(Gateway API)"]
    GatewayCtrl -->|creates| KAP["kube-auth-proxy<br/>Deployment"]
    GatewayCtrl -->|creates| EF["EnvoyFilter<br/>(ext_authz)"]
    GatewayCtrl -->|creates| DR["DestinationRule<br/>(TLS)"]
    GatewayCtrl -->|creates| OAuthClient["OAuthClient"]

    %% Monitoring creates
    MonitoringCtrl -->|creates| MonStack["MonitoringStack<br/>Thanos, Tempo,<br/>OTEL Collector"]

    %% Component controllers deploy via kustomize
    DashCtrl -->|deploys via<br/>kustomize| Manifests["/opt/manifests/"]

    %% External dependencies
    DSCCtrl -->|API calls| K8sAPI["Kubernetes API<br/>6443/TCP"]
    GatewayCtrl -->|depends on| OCPIngress["OpenShift<br/>Gateway Controller"]

